    "en": {
      "title": "2021 A/L Top Ranks \u2013 Results available online",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); \u00a062% of students who sat for the 2021 G. C. E. Advanced Level Examination have qualified for University Entrance.",
        "Ishara Lakmal Heenkenda of Kendagolla Maha Vidyalaya in Badulla was ranked the first in the island in the Arts stream at the G.C.E. Advanced Level examination 2021.",
        "Ishara Lakmal hails from the remote Muthumala Village in Badulla.",
        "Neranda Dilhara Kumarasinghe of Mayurapada Central College in Narammala became the island\u2019s first in the Technology stream.",
        "At the same time, I. B. U. N. Irugalbandara was ranked 4th in the Technology stream, and he too is from the Mayurapada Central College in Narammala.",
        "Sahan Samarakoon of Royal College, Colombo was ranked first in Maths Stream.",
        "Ishini Neha Amararatne of Ratnavali Balika Vidyalaya, Gampaha was ranked first in the island in the Commerce stream.",
        "Thamilvannan Thuwaragesh of St. Michael\u2019s College, Batticaloa was ranked first in the Biological Science stream.",
        "The results of the 2021 G.C.E. Advanced Level examination were released online through the websites: www.doenets.lk | www.results.exams.gov.lk",
        "Sri Lanka calls for EOI for SriLankan Catering & Ground Handling"
      ],
